(49, 'knayashree', 'KANYASHREE', '<p>&lsquo;KANYASHREE PRAKALPA&rsquo; has been started from first October, 2013 in this Block. Girl students in the age group of 13 to 18 years in the current financial year &amp; reading in between class VIII to XII are eligible to get the benefit of this scheme.</p>\n<p>Girl Students reading in Colleges/Training Institutes are also eligible for the scheme. But their age must be not less than 18 years and not greater than or equal &nbsp;to 19 years.</p>\n<p>The Annual Family Income of the applicant must be less than Rs.1,20,000/-(One lakh twenty thousand). The applicant must be Unmarried at the time of application.</p>\n<p>Application forms are available in the concerned School / College / Training Institute under this Block.</p>\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong><a href="http://www.wbkanyashree.gov.in" target="_blank">READ MORE</a></strong></p>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
